org.mini2Dx.gettext.antlr

Interface GetTextListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GetTextBaseListener, PoFile

    public interface GetTextListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by GetTextParser.
